# node-linker=hoisted produces a flat node_modules tree (no symlinks). The
# runtime image COPYs node_modules between stages and symlinks break that
# pattern; hoisted layout sidesteps the issue and matches what the previous
# bun layout exposed to downstream tooling.
node-linker=hoisted
# Pin to exact versions on `pnpm add`; matches the existing convention from
# the bun config.
save-exact=true
